===Pronunciation===
:(US) SAMPA:/pO.li.gOn/

===Etymology===
Greek polygonal; many + angle: compare French ''[[polygone]]''

===Noun===
Plural: '''polygons'''
#''(Geometry):'' A plane figure having many angles, and consequently many sides; esp., one whose perimeter consists of more than four sides; any figure having many angles.

